node.title: Person found dead at Hamilton's Frankton train station
node.description: A Hamilton train station has been cordoned off after a person was found dead this morning.
node.content:
["A Hamilton train station has been cordoned off after a person was found dead this morning.", "", "
Frankton station is a passenger station where the Te Kuia train from Hamilton to Auckland departs. Photo: RNZ / Leah Tebbutt
", "Police said emergency services were called to the scene at Frankton train station shortly after 8am.", "St John earlier said six vehicles attended the incident in Frankton, and an ambulance was on the scene.", "The death was expected to be referred to the coroner and police said a routine scene examination was underway."]
